==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Glomeration
<hw>Glom`er*a"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>glomeratio</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of forming or gathering into a ball or round
mass; the state of being gathered into a ball; conglomeration.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which is formed into a ball; a ball.</def>
<rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Glomerous</ent>⟦br⟧
